'''Shadowroot soap''' was made from a rare plant called the [[shadowroot plant]]. When the soap was put into water and washed on an object, the object became invisible, but it could be brought back when washed with clean water. [[Logray/Legends|Logray]] had a bar of shadowroot soap that was stolen by the [[Dulok/Legends|Duloks]] thinking it was a bar of [[Ewok soap]].

